author: Rakesh Mohan Chaturvedi
title: BJP Concerned at Mass Reverse Migration to UP, Bihar and MP
description: Decides to not indulge in any blame game, making efforts to deal with this ‘unprecedented and panic-like’ situation
content: New Delhi: The mass gathering of migrants from Bihar, Uttar Pradesh and Madhya Pradesh in the national capital on Saturday and their attempt to walk hundreds of miles to reach their native place has posed a serious challenge, feel several BJP leaders. However… [+2437 chars]
